<p>Alleged torture and ill-treatment of 11 individuals by Border Security Forces (BSF) in 
</p>
<p>the West Bengal Region. According to the information received, medical personnel in 
</p>
<p>the areas concerned refused to examine Mr. X, Mr. Mondal Chhanarul, Mr. Sardar 
</p>
