</p>
<p>necessary tests. Mr. X&#8217;s passport was allegedly impounded by the immigration 
</p>
<p>authorities for two hours until the next available flight. During this time, his phone 
</p>
<p>was allegedly taken from him, and he was unable to make any calls. He was escorted 
</p>
<p>to a detention room by the police and required to pay 61.00 Singapore dollars towards 
</p>
<p>&#8216;security fees&#8217;, the details of which were not disclosed to him.  
