<p>Alleged execution in secret of four ethnic Arab men from Ahvaz, who were facing the 
</p>
<p>death penalty. According to the information received, Mr. Ghazi Abasi, Mr. 
</p>
<p>Abdolreza Amir Khanafereh, Mr. Abdolamir Mojadami and Mr. Jasem Moghadam 
</p>
<p>Panah, were sentenced to death on charges of Mahrebeh (enmity against God) and 
</p>
