</p>
<p>other ill-treatment. An appeal was reportedly still outstanding when the execution was 
</p>
<p>carried out. On 2 December 2013, officials from the Ministry of Intelligence informed 
</p>
<p>the families of the four men about their execution. Neither the family nor the lawyer 
</p>
