</p>
<p>Alleged imposition of the death penalty on a Mexican national in violation of 
</p>
<p>international human rights standards. According to the information received, Mr. 
</p>
<p>Edgar Arias Tamayo was sentenced to death for the murder of Officer Guy Gaddis of 
</p>
<p>the Houston Police Department, allegedly committed in 1994 in Texas when he was 
</p>
<p>26 years old. Mr. Arias Tamayo had the right to seek consular assistance after arrest. 
</p>
