</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Follow up to the joint allegation letter OTH 4/2013 dated 4 April 2013 addressed to 
</p>
<p>IAMGOLD Corporation in relation to its alleged activities in Suriname. In the letter, the 
</p>
<p>Working Group and the Special Rapporteur thank IAMGOLD for its response dated 5 
</p>
<p>June 2013 and its willingness to engage on this issue. The Working Group and Special 
</p>
<p>Rapporteur also provide IAMGOLD with further information on the communications 
</p>
<p>procedure of special procedures of the Human Rights Council. The Special Rapporteur 
</p>
<p>further refers to earlier comments on this case published in his last annual report to the 
</p>
<p>Human Rights Council on communications sent, observations and replies received 
</p>
<p>(A/HRC/24/41/Add.4). 
</p>
<p>11/02/2014 
