</p>
<p> <b>101 
</b></p>
<p><b>Appendix 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Mandates of special procedures  
</b></p>
<p><i>Mandate title 
</i></p>
<p><i>Human Rights 
</i></p>
<p><i>Council 
</i></p>
<p><i>resolution 
</i></p>
<p>Special Rapporteur on adequate housing as a component of the right to an adequate 
standard of living, and on the right to non-discrimination in this context 
</p>
